<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨٨ -<span class="c5"> وَعَن عبد الله بن زيد:</span> <span class="c1">" رَأَيْت رَسُول الله صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّم َ <span class="c4">[٧ / أ]</span> يتَوَضَّأ فَأخذ لأذنيه مَاء خلاف المَاء الَّذِي أَخذ لرأسه "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٨٩ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْبَيْهَقِيّ:</span> <span class="c1">" إِسْنَاده صَحِيح "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(فصل فِي ضعيفه)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٩٠ - مِنْهُ،<span class="c5"> حَدِيث:</span> <span class="c1">" الأذنان من الرَّأْس "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>